---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'June 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Legal Notices — Pss.Orange"
  description="Terms of use, disclaimers, and legal notices for the Pss.Orange website."
>
  <main class="pt-20">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="dark-gradient-header">
      <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-3xl text-white" data-aos="fade-up">
          <p class="text-emerald-400 text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Legal</p>
          <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4">
            Legal Notices
          </h1>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Content -->
    <section class="py-20">
      <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-10">

          <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h2 class="text-white font-bold text-xl mb-4">1. Website Terms of Use</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
              Welcome to pssorange.com (the "Website"), operated by Power Systems &amp; Solutions Co., Ltd.
              ("Pss.Orange", "we", "our", or "us"). By accessing and using this Website, you agree to
              be bound by these Legal Notices. If you do not agree, please do not use this Website.
            </p>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mt-4">
              We grant you a limited, personal, non-exclusive, non-transferable licence to access and
              view the content of this Website for your own personal, non-commercial use only. You may
              not reproduce, distribute, modify, create derivative works from, or commercially exploit
              any content on this Website without our prior written consent.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h2 class="text-white font-bold text-xl mb-4">2. No Investment Advice</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
              The content on this Website is provided for general informational purposes only and does
              not constitute investment advice, financial advice, a solicitation, or an offer to buy or
              sell any securities, funds, or financial instruments. Nothing on this Website should be
              relied upon as the basis for any investment or financial decision.
            </p>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mt-4">
              Pss.Orange is an independent renewable energy developer, EPC contractor, and asset manager.
              Any references to returns, project performance, or capacity figures are historical or
              indicative in nature and are not a guarantee of future performance or results.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h2 class="text-white font-bold text-xl mb-4">3. Forward-Looking Statements</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
              Certain statements on this Website may be forward-looking, including those relating to
              project pipelines, capacity targets, geographic expansion, and strategic objectives. These
              statements involve known and unknown risks and uncertainties and are based on current
              expectations and assumptions. Actual outcomes may differ materially from those expressed
              or implied. Pss.Orange undertakes no obligation to update forward-looking statements to
              reflect changed circumstances or new information.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h2 class="text-white font-bold text-xl mb-4">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
              All content on this Website — including text, graphics, logos, images, project data,
              and design — is the property of Power Systems &amp; Solutions Co., Ltd. or its content
              suppliers and is protected by applicable intellectual property laws. The Pss.Orange name,
              logo, and brand elements are trademarks of Power Systems &amp; Solutions Co., Ltd. and
              may not be used without our prior written permission.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h2 class="text-white font-bold text-xl mb-4">5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
              To the fullest extent permitted by applicable law, Pss.Orange and its affiliates, officers,
              directors, employees, and agents shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special,
              consequential, or punitive damages arising out of or related to your use of, or inability
              to use, this Website or its content. We make no warranties, express or implied, regarding
              the accuracy, completeness, reliability, or suitability of the information on this Website.
            </p>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mt-4">
              This Website may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the
              content, privacy practices, or accuracy of information on any third-party site. Links do
              not imply endorsement.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h2 class="text-white font-bold text-xl mb-4">6. Governing Law</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
              These Legal Notices and any disputes arising from your use of this Website shall be
              governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the Kingdom of Thailand, without
              regard to conflict of law principles. You agree to submit to the exclusive jurisdiction
              of the courts of Bangkok, Thailand for the resolution of any such disputes.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h2 class="text-white font-bold text-xl mb-4">7. Changes to These Notices</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
              We reserve the right to update these Legal Notices at any time. Material changes will
              be reflected by updating the "Last updated" date at the top of this page. Your continued
              use of the Website following any changes constitutes your acceptance of the revised notices.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h2 class="text-white font-bold text-xl mb-4">8. Contact</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
              For any legal enquiries relating to this Website or its content, please contact us at:
            </p>
            <div class="mt-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-slate-800/50 text-sm text-slate-300 space-y-1">
              <p class="font-semibold text-white">Power Systems &amp; Solutions Co., Ltd. (Pss.Orange)</p>
              <p>Ocean Tower 2 (26th Floor), 75/56 Sukhumvit Soi 19, Bangkok 10110, Thailand</p>
              <p>
                Email:&nbsp;
                <a href="mailto:info@pssorange.com" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 transition-colors" style="min-height: auto;">
                  info@pssorange.com
                </a>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
